[package]
name = "alacritty_terminal"
version = "0.24.1-dev"
authors = [ "Christian Duerr <contact@christianduerr.com>", "Joe Wilm <joe@jwilm.com>",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "Library for writing terminal emulators"
readme = "../README.md"
homepage = "https://alacritty.org"
repository = "https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70.0"

[features]
default = [ "serde",]
serde = [ "dep:serde", "bitflags/serde", "vte/serde",]

[dependencies]
base64 = "0.22.0"
bitflags = "2.4.1"
home = "0.5.5"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
parking_lot = "0.12.0"
polling = "3.0.0"
regex-automata = "0.4.3"
unicode-width = "0.1"

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.0"

[dependencies.vte]
version = "0.13.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "ansi", "serde",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive", "rc",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies]
rustix-openpty = "0.1.1"
signal-hook = "0.3.10"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
piper = "0.2.1"
miow = "0.6.0"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.52.0"
features = [ "Win32_System_Console", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Security", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_WindowsProgramming",]

[package]
categories = [ "gui",]
description = "Types for handling UI scaling"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "DPI", "HiDPI", "scale-factor",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
name = "dpi"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
rust-version = "1.73"
version = "0.1.1"

[features]
mint = [ "dep:mint",]
serde = [ "dep:serde",]

[dependencies.mint]
optional = true
version = "0.5.6"

[dependencies.serde]
optional = true
version = "1"
features = [ "serde_derive",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "mint", "serde",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
targets = [ "i686-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc", "aarch64-apple-darwin", "x86_64-apple-darwin", "i686-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu", "aarch64-apple-ios", "aarch64-linux-android", "wasm32-unknown-unknown",]

[workspace]
resolver = "2"
members = [ "renderer", "vello", "vger", "tiny_skia", "reactive", "editor-core", "examples/*",]

[package]
name = "floem"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "The Floem contributors",]
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/lapce/floem"
description = "A native Rust UI library with fine-grained reactivity"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.85"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
slotmap = "1.0"
sha2 = "0.10"
bitflags = "2.9"
indexmap = "2"
rustc-hash = "2.1"
smallvec = "1.15"
educe = "0.6"
raw-window-handle = "0.6.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.10"
im-rc = "15.1.0"

[features]
default = [ "editor", "default-image-formats", "vger",]
vello = [ "dep:floem_vello_renderer",]
vger = [ "dep:floem_vger_renderer",]
serde = [ "dep:serde", "winit/serde", "peniko/serde", "lapce-xi-rope/serde", "smallvec/serde", "floem-editor-core?/serde",]
editor = [ "floem-editor-core", "dep:lapce-xi-rope", "dep:strum", "dep:strum_macros", "dep:downcast-rs",]
default-image-formats = [ "image-jpeg", "image-ico", "image-png", "image-webp",]
image-avif = [ "image/avif",]
image-bmp = [ "image/bmp",]
image-dds = [ "image/dds",]
image-exr = [ "image/exr",]
image-ff = [ "image/ff",]
image-gif = [ "image/gif",]
image-hdr = [ "image/hdr",]
image-ico = [ "image/ico",]
image-jpeg = [ "image/jpeg",]
image-png = [ "image/png",]
image-pnm = [ "image/pnm",]
image-qoi = [ "image/qoi",]
image-tga = [ "image/tga",]
image-tiff = [ "image/tiff",]
image-webp = [ "image/webp",]
tokio = [ "dep:tokio",]
rfd-async-std = [ "dep:rfd", "rfd/async-std",]
rfd-tokio = [ "dep:rfd", "rfd/tokio",]
futures = [ "dep:futures",]
crossbeam = [ "dep:crossbeam", "floem_renderer/crossbeam",]

[workspace.package]
license = "MIT"
version = "0.2.0"

[workspace.dependencies]
raw-window-handle = "0.6.0"

[dependencies.taffy]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "grid",]

[dependencies.rfd]
version = "0.15"
default-features = false
features = [ "xdg-portal",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = [ "sync", "rt",]
optional = true

[dependencies.peniko]
version = "0.4.0"

[dependencies.serde]
optional = true
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.lapce-xi-rope]
optional = true
version = "0.3.2"

[dependencies.strum]
optional = true
version = "0.27"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.strum_macros]
optional = true
version = "0.27"

[dependencies.downcast-rs]
version = "2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.floem_renderer]
path = "renderer"
version = "0.2.0"

[dependencies.floem_vello_renderer]
path = "vello"
version = "0.2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.floem_vger_renderer]
path = "vger"
version = "0.2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.floem_tiny_skia_renderer]
path = "tiny_skia"
version = "0.2.0"

[dependencies.floem_reactive]
path = "reactive"
version = "0.2.0"

[dependencies.floem-editor-core]
path = "editor-core"
version = "0.2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.copypasta]
version = "0.10"
default-features = false
features = [ "wayland", "x11",]

[dependencies.parking_lot]
version = "0.12"

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
default-features = false

[dependencies.im]
version = "15.1.0"

[dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
rev = "ee245c569d65fdeacf705ee5eedb564508d10ebe"

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.31"
optional = true

[dependencies.crossbeam]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[workspace.dependencies.peniko]
version = "0.4.0"

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"

[workspace.dependencies.lapce-xi-rope]
version = "0.3.2"

[workspace.dependencies.strum]
version = "0.27"
features = [ "derive",]

[workspace.dependencies.strum_macros]
version = "0.27"

[workspace.dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.im]
version = "15.1.0"

[workspace.dependencies.resvg]
version = "0.45.1"

[workspace.dependencies.wgpu]
version = "24.0.5"

[workspace.dependencies.parking_lot]
version = "0.12"

[workspace.dependencies.swash]
version = "0.2.5"

[workspace.dependencies.muda]
git = "https://github.com/tauri-apps/muda"
rev = "8e986af3cea96a729413abc75c3702dec3990bd2"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
rev = "ee245c569d65fdeacf705ee5eedb564508d10ebe"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies]
web-time = "1"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies]
clipboard-win = "3.1.1"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"windows\", target_os = \"macos\"))".dependencies.muda]
git = "https://github.com/tauri-apps/muda"
rev = "8e986af3cea96a729413abc75c3702dec3990bd2"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.wasm-bindgen-futures]
version = "0.4"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.wgpu]
version = "24.0.5"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2]
version = "0.6"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-foundation]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-app-kit]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "NSApplication", "NSResponder",]

[package]
name = "floem-editor-core"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/lapce/floem"
license = "MIT"
description = "The core of the floem text editor"

[dependencies]
itertools = "0.14.0"
bitflags = "2.4.2"
memchr = "2.7.1"

[features]
serde = [ "dep:serde",]

[dependencies.serde]
optional = true
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.27"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.strum_macros]
version = "0.27"

[dependencies.lapce-xi-rope]
version = "0.3.2"

[workspace]
resolver = "2"

[package]
name = "floem-vger"
description = "Unofficial vger fork for Floem"
version = "0.3.1"
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
authors = [ "Taylor Holliday <taylor@audulus.com>",]
repository = "https://github.com/audulus/vger-rs"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
wgpu = "24.0.5"
euclid = "0.22.11"
fontdue = "0.9.3"
rect_packer = "0.2.1"
cosmic-text = "0.14.2"

[dev-dependencies]
png = "0.17.16"
futures = "0.3"
futures-intrusive = "0.5"
svg = "0.13.1"
rand = "0.8.5"

[package]
name = "floem_reactive"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/lapce/floem"
description = "A native Rust UI library with fine-grained reactivity"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
smallvec = "1.10.0"

[package]
name = "floem_renderer"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/lapce/floem"
description = "A native Rust UI library with fine-grained reactivity"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
futures = "0.3.31"

[features]
crossbeam = [ "dep:crossbeam",]

[dependencies.parking_lot]
version = "0.12"

[dependencies.peniko]
version = "0.4.0"

[dependencies.resvg]
version = "0.45.1"

[dependencies.swash]
version = "0.2.5"

[dependencies.cosmic-text]
version = "0.14.2"
features = [ "shape-run-cache",]

[dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
rev = "ee245c569d65fdeacf705ee5eedb564508d10ebe"

[dependencies.wgpu]
version = "24.0.5"

[dependencies.crossbeam]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.wasm-bindgen-futures]
version = "0.4"

[package]
name = "floem_tiny_skia_renderer"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/lapce/floem"
description = "A native Rust UI library with fine-grained reactivity"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
raw-window-handle = "0.6.0"
anyhow = "1.0.69"
softbuffer = "0.4.1"

[dependencies.peniko]
version = "0.4.0"

[dependencies.resvg]
version = "0.45.1"

[dependencies.floem_renderer]
path = "../renderer"
version = "0.2.0"

[package]
name = "floem_vger_renderer"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/lapce/floem"
description = "A native Rust UI library with fine-grained reactivity"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0"

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
default-features = false

[dependencies.resvg]
version = "0.45.1"

[dependencies.peniko]
version = "0.4.0"

[dependencies.wgpu]

[dependencies.floem-vger-rs]
git = "https://github.com/lapce/vger-rs.git"
rev = "3206d47ec1e30b645ddcb0687036ba3e1f0d98ec"
version = "0.3.1"
package = "floem-vger"

[dependencies.floem_renderer]
path = "../renderer"
version = "0.2.0"

[package]
name = "human-sort"
version = "0.2.2"
authors = [ "Vlad Nagikh <paradakh@protonmail.com>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/paradakh/human-sort"
description = "Human sort (natural sort) implementation"
keywords = [ "sort", "natural", "human", "order",]
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2018"
categories = [ "algorithms",]

[dependencies]

[badges.travis-ci]
repository = "paradakh/human-sort"
branch = "master"

[package]
name = "locale_config"
version = "0.3.1-alpha.0"
description = "Maintains locale preferences for process and thread and initialises them by\ninspecting the system for user preference.\n"
authors = [ "Jan Hudec <bulb@ucw.cz>",]
license = "MIT"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/locale_config/"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-locale/locale_config/"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "i18n",]
categories = [ "os",]
exclude = [ "/ci/*", "/.travis.yml", "/appveyor.yml",]

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1"
regex = "1"

[badges.travis-ci]
repository = "rust-locale/locale_config"

[badges.appveyor]
repository = "rust-locale/locale_config"

[package.metadata.release]
upload-doc = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
objc2 = "0.5.1"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "winnls",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-foundation]
version = "0.2"
features = [ "NSLocale", "NSString",]

[package]
name = "lsp-types"
version = "0.95.1"
authors = [ "Markus Westerlind <marwes91@gmail.com>", "Bruno Medeiros <bruno.do.medeiros@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "Types for interaction with a language server, using VSCode's Language Server Protocol"
repository = "https://github.com/gluon-lang/lsp-types"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/lsp-types"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "language", "server", "lsp", "vscode", "lsif",]
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0.1"
serde_json = "1.0.50"
serde_repr = "0.1"

[features]
default = []
proposed = []

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.34"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.0.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[package]
name = "muda"
version = "0.16.1"
description = "Menu Utilities for Desktop Applications"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "windowing", "menu",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/amrbashir/muda"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/muda"
categories = [ "gui",]
rust-version = "1.71"

[features]
default = [ "libxdo", "gtk",]
libxdo = [ "dep:libxdo",]
gtk = [ "dep:gtk",]
common-controls-v6 = []
serde = [ "dep:serde", "dpi/serde",]

[dependencies]
crossbeam-channel = "0.5"
keyboard-types = "0.7"
once_cell = "1"
thiserror = "2"
dpi = "0.1"

[dev-dependencies]
winit = "0.30"
tao = "0.30"
wry = "0.45"
image = "0.25"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
objc2 = "0.6.0"
png = "0.17"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.59"
features = [ "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_UI_Shell", "Win32_Globalization", "Win32_UI_Input_KeyboardAndMouse", "Win32_System_SystemServices", "Win32_UI_Accessibility", "Win32_UI_HiDpi", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_UI_Controls",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.gtk]
version = "0.18"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.libxdo]
version = "0.6.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-core-foundation]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "std", "CFCGTypes",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-foundation]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "std", "NSAttributedString", "NSData", "NSDictionary", "NSGeometry", "NSString", "NSThread",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-app-kit]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "std", "objc2-core-foundation", "NSApplication", "NSCell", "NSEvent", "NSImage", "NSMenu", "NSMenuItem", "NSResponder", "NSRunningApplication", "NSView", "NSWindow",]

[package]
name = "psp-types"
version = "0.1.0"
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "Types for interaction with plugin server protocol"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.lsp-types]
version = "0"
features = [ "proposed",]

[workspace]
members = [ "regalloc2-tool",]

[package]
name = "regalloc2"
version = "0.9.3"
authors = [ "Chris Fallin <chris@cfallin.org>", "Mozilla SpiderMonkey Developers",]
edition = "2018"
license = "Apache-2.0 WITH LLVM-exception"
description = "Backtracking register allocator inspired from IonMonkey"
repository = "https://github.com/bytecodealliance/regalloc2"

[features]
default = [ "std",]
std = []
checker = []
trace-log = []
fuzzing = [ "libfuzzer-sys", "checker", "trace-log",]
enable-serde = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4.8"
default-features = false

[dependencies.smallvec]
version = "1.6.1"
features = [ "union",]

[dependencies.rustc-hash]
version = "1.1.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.slice-group-by]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.hashbrown]
version = "0.14"
features = [ "ahash",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.136"
features = [ "derive", "alloc",]
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.libfuzzer-sys]
version = "0.4.2"
optional = true

[profile.release]

[package]

license = "MIT"

[lib]

[dependencies.darling]
version = "0.14"

[dependencies.proc-macro2]
version = "1"

[dependencies.quote]
version = "1.0.14"

[dependencies.syn]

[package]
name = "tracing"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Eliza Weisman <eliza@buoyant.io>", "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"
homepage = "https://tokio.rs"
description = "Application-level tracing for Rust.\n"
categories = [ "development-tools::debugging", "development-tools::profiling", "asynchronous", "no-std",]
keywords = [ "logging", "tracing", "metrics", "async",]
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.63.0"

[dependencies]
pin-project-lite = "0.2.9"

[dev-dependencies]
log = "0.4.17"

[features]
default = [ "std", "attributes",]
max_level_off = []
max_level_error = []
max_level_warn = []
max_level_info = []
max_level_debug = []
max_level_trace = []
release_max_level_off = []
release_max_level_error = []
release_max_level_warn = []
release_max_level_info = []
release_max_level_debug = []
release_max_level_trace = []
alloc = [ "tracing-core/alloc",]
std = [ "tracing-core/std", "alloc",]
log-always = [ "log",]
attributes = [ "tracing-attributes",]

[dependencies.tracing-core]
path = "../tracing-core"
version = "0.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4.17"
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing-attributes]
path = "../tracing-attributes"
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.3.6"
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.21"
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.tracing-mock]
path = "../tracing-mock"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.3.38"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[[bench]]
name = "bench"
harness = false

[package]
name = "tracing-appender"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Zeki Sherif <zekshi@amazon.com>", "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"
homepage = "https://tokio.rs"
description = "Provides utilities for file appenders and making non-blocking writers.\n"
categories = [ "development-tools::debugging", "asynchronous",]
keywords = [ "logging", "tracing", "file-appender", "non-blocking-writer",]
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.53.0"

[dependencies]
crossbeam-channel = "0.5.5"
thiserror = "1.0.31"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.3.0"

[dependencies.time]
version = "0.3.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "formatting", "parsing",]

[dependencies.parking_lot]
optional = true
version = "0.12.1"

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
